subject: New Automatic Tool For Converting JUnit3 TestCases to JUnit4
msgSnippet: Hello everyone! I ve recently uploaded an automatic tool that converts junit3 to junit4. More information and the tool itself can be found at junit-converter
messageBody:
Hello everyone!

I've recently uploaded an automatic tool that converts junit3 to junit4.
More information and the tool itself can be found at junit-converter
<http://junit-converter.sf.net> 's site.

Waiting for your feedback,
Aviv Ben-Yosef.
